hkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20130807%2F238308%2F&d=4cPfoMSL9U39dwI9uzNim54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=be4f3dc2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20130807/238308/</a>"},{"pid":"6a92f2746af5fd41e6002592eaf82fef36d7cd18","tid":410783,"uid":125079,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:18:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【綜合報導】日本大阪市2名20多歲消防員因日前被爆出拍攝男同志系列A片，昨日相關高層祭出處分，將2人停職6個月。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，2人在去年8月於一處海水浴場，被AV星探挖掘，但2人表明不想拍攝與AV女優做愛的畫面，因此星探將2人安排拍同志片。在上月26日，有人將DVD和告發文送到消防署，2人拍同志A片的事情才曝光。<br />\n<br />\n日本媒體報導指出，到今年3月為止，這2名消防員靠拍A片賺進7萬日圓(約新台幣2.1萬元)收入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/i mages/ReNews/20130807/640_8f60f7ea40ed2f6e61dcc04de5e4c5c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fi%20mages%2FReNews%2F20130807%2F640_8f60f7ea40ed2f6e61dcc04de5e4c5c5.jpg&h=56ccb809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20130807/238308/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20130807%2F238308%2F&d=4cPfoMSL9U39dwI9uzNim54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=be4f3dc2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20130807/238308/</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有人將DVD和告發文送到消防署，係咪代表佢地識既人當中有睇 gay 片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a99bb53d2ec5801d85ded6d13e39a080df3079","tid":410783,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:18:41.000Z","msg":"link"},{"pid":"1fff28bf9a87bca8d684a6ba4873bb36f178376f","tid":410783,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:19:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d054e33bbd278628ab433307d10d63fa3016194","tid":410783,"uid":20130,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":